<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一、明秀园服战队老板传音互撕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200913/e57b88c77a3948b5a016e6f5ebdfe7bf.png" max-width="600" /></p>
